video.title: Love Naggers
video.synopsis: From the quirky to the scandalous, any relationship is fair game for a panel of love experts who comb over text messages and revel in reenactments.

episodes.synopsis: She's over his rude remarks and violent behavior, but he insists it's all because of love. The MCs aren't buying his story. They are up in arms... and legs!
You said what to your boyfriend?! Honesty is fine, but overdoing it is rude. Relationship hits a bump when she gets a job. Why is the boss buying her drinks?
He always has to be right. She felt hurt, so he tells her she's wrong? This is sick. Wedding is postponed but they are okay. Then a mysterious necklace appears.
Pranks are fun, but not if they send you to the hospital. This girl's a devil! They were happy until learning that his step-mom is the mother that left her.
I want you all to myself! Is he sweet or sour? He acts more oddly over time. This guy wants to dominate, he even tells her how to talk. Who does he think he is?
Can you buy me that? Can you lend me some money? This guy is totally shameless. This story triggers a trauma from Wu-jae's past. Never date a dirty moocher!
The boyfriend disappears in the middle of the night. So suspicious! Her woman's instinct is on full alert. Does he have another girl? Or some dark secret?
She receives a very sweet, moving proposal from the boyfriend. Then a woman calls â€” can she trust him? What is he hiding, a second girlfriend in the wings?
He's sweet by day and hot at night! But suddenly it's over. Oh, wait... Now he wants me back. Does he remember what he said? Does he have a split personality?
She should have known. The boyfriend acts sweet but abruptly turns sour. He begs advice then blames her for his failings, and even drops a bombshell. Lose him!
I have a good idea, she says. Oh no, not again! Her pranks always cross the line. Please don't, he pleads. But the girlfriend just goes ahead! He's dumbfounded!
The boyfriend's business failed! No matter what she says, he's Mr. Grumpy. The girlfriend drops money like water to look cute on social media. But whose money?
A boyfriend who prefers fit women and has no tact about losing weight; a boyfriend who makes other women feel a little too special. They must have a reason!
You're all so gorgeous! Her boyfriend keeps flirting with her friends. When confronted, he claims he's done nothing. Seems suspicious! But is it on purpose?
Why is he avoiding me? Why does he lie? The truth is as absurd as the boyfriend! I'm dating my secret crush, but now it feels like we're in the friend zone.
I want you to be my muse. She thought he was being romantic, but then she saw his pictures! His girlfriend's become distant. Is it really about the age gap?
Her boyfriend's not convinced. She changes her phobias conveniently and often! It's his first one, but he's sure girlfriends shouldn't hang around other guys.
Her wonderful boyfriend has been hiding many secrets. Nobody will let this go! His girlfriend's been supporting him for years and in return, she gets dumped.
Her bets on him were cute at first! This time his girlfriend's crossed a line. What's her plan? And a big misunderstanding puts a lovey-dovey couple in crisis!
Surprise! An explicit gift for one boyfriend goes poorly. His girlfriend's suspicions lead her down an unexpected path after demanding she return the items.
Obey me! Someone's got a Napoleon complex, and he's taking it out on his girlfriend. Can a couple get some privacy please?! This third wheel is out of control.
Her boyfriend sounds so sweet! But is she really the only girl for him? After leaving to help another woman get home, maybe not. And the photo doesn't help!
Her boyfriend invited her over but for a different kind of nail. What's he hiding? One poor man falls for a big spender but no longer has a job to support her!
His girlfriend used to be shy, but recently she's been acting out inappropriately! Her boyfriend supports her art, but recent inspiration has him frustrated.
"The" Min-ju shows up unexpectedly. Is this the woman her boyfriend keeps mentioning? From cold feet to an affair, his girlfriend's elusive past is unveiled.
Office romance rumors have one girlfriend stalking her own boyfriend for answers. And one woman discovers her real-life boyfriend has an online girlfriend!
Excited for a fresh start, the college couple ends up in a love triangle. Will the girlfriend's feelings change? Can't wait for the conclusion of this drama!
The girlfriend of her boyfriend's brother ruins the happiest day of her life in an entangled love square. Getting hitched after a few weeks? Put the brakes on!
He has a hard time dating because his friend keeps meddling. When she admits her true feelings for him, they happily date... until the truth reveals itself!
There's always a price to pay when it comes to good looks â€” or so, one woman thought! Her mind changed after meeting a cute guy, but is he also changing her?
